{
  "stem": "3928.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I mean, it's-- we try to do whatever we can to help people whom we can help.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And but the same time, it's a very thankless task, sometime.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I have a lady, her name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Harsanyi.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saved one of her son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I saved one of her daughter, who, right now, lives in Israeli if she's still alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after the war, the same lady looked at, in my face, and she told me, you killed my son, because I could not save the other son, because she told me where she was.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when I went there, they was already moved away, you know, the-- the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this woman, whom I saved two of her children, because I could not save the third one, she told me, right in my face, you killed my son.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now you know how I felt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had certain downside of it, too, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- my worst nightmare was when I find out, after the war, from a person who told me that, Les, I lost my wife, because I didn't have money to buy the paper from Mr.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schweikert.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I told him, what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I gave the paper to give it to the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I risked my life to save people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I risked everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For every time I saved a person, I risked my own life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I gave a paper away, you know, if they would have come, it was the same way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I did not realize there were people who profited by, instead of giving it, they try to sell.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jewish people were selling it to Jewish people, try to sell the paper, which was-- I was very much appalled with, because this happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
